'''Soul Fysh''' is a {{2|Bosses|Boss}} found in the {{2|Underdocks}}.

== Pattern ==
{{Intents|Soul Fysh|2}}
The Soul Fysh repeats the same five moves in order:
# {{Int|Soul Fysh|Beckon||2}}
# {{Int|Soul Fysh|De-Gas||2}}
# {{Int|Soul Fysh|Gaze||2}}
# {{Int|Soul Fysh|Fade||2}}
# {{Int|Soul Fysh|Scream||2}}

== Notes ==
*The first iteration of {{Int|Soul Fysh|Fade||2}}'s {{KW|Intangible||2}} fades instantly during the transition from {{2|Soul Fysh}}'s turn to the player's. It effectively gains just 1 {{KW|Intangible||2}}.
